00:21:58,940 --> 00:22:02,320
 Prvo pitanje,

452
00:22:02,320 --> 00:22:03,520
 dakle, autoritet,

453
00:22:03,520 --> 00:22:04,720
 sigurno da,

454
00:22:04,720 --> 00:22:05,500
 da, da, evo,

455
00:22:05,500 --> 00:22:07,700
 Bog daje, evo,

