00:22:18,720 --> 00:22:19,620
 si Isus rodio,

465
00:22:20,480 --> 00:22:21,300
 sa požičevo,

466
00:22:21,300 --> 00:22:23,140
 koliko bi ljudi

467
00:22:23,140 --> 00:22:23,980
 vodjeli,

468
00:22:23,980 --> 00:22:24,980
 vodjeli da,

469
00:22:24,980 --> 00:22:25,800
 da budu

470
00:22:25,800 --> 00:22:26,940
 ovdje u Betlehemu.

471
00:22:26,940 --> 00:22:27,720
 Dakle,

472
00:22:27,720 --> 00:22:28,840
 biti,

473
00:22:28,840 --> 00:22:29,620
 biti ovdje

474
00:22:29,620 --> 00:22:30,940
 kao Hrvat,

475
00:22:30,940 --> 00:22:32,240
 je doista, evo,

476
00:22:32,240 --> 00:22:33,980
 i ponos nama svima ovdje,

477
00:22:33,980 --> 00:22:36,400
 jer malo prije smo spomenuli,

478
00:22:36,400 --> 00:22:37,780
 Hrvatska je doista prisutna

479
00:22:37,780 --> 00:22:38,660
 u svetoj zemlji,

480
00:22:38,660 --> 00:22:39,900
 preko Franjevaca,

481
00:22:39,900 --> 00:22:40,840
