00:22:50,480 --> 00:22:51,480
 To je mene

490
00:22:51,480 --> 00:22:52,440
 u svu doista pomoglo

491
00:22:52,440 --> 00:22:53,620
 i kad sam prije studirao

492
00:22:53,620 --> 00:22:54,380
 u Jeruzalemu,

493
00:22:54,380 --> 00:22:55,940
 ali sada,

494
00:22:55,940 --> 00:22:57,100
 naravno,

495
00:22:57,100 --> 00:22:57,740
 kroz

496
00:22:57,740 --> 00:22:59,840
 studiju ovdje,

497
00:22:59,840 --> 00:23:00,880
 arapskog jezika,

498
00:23:00,880 --> 00:23:01,740
 klasični okred,

499
00:23:01,740 --> 00:23:02,260
