535
00:23:48,960 --> 00:23:50,460
 pomaganje kršćanima

536
00:23:50,460 --> 00:23:51,560
 da ostane svetoj zemlji,

537
00:23:51,560 --> 00:23:52,660
 pa onda

538
00:23:52,660 --> 00:23:54,600
 od operacija

539
00:23:54,600 --> 00:23:56,820
 i mnošto drugih programa

540
00:23:56,820 --> 00:23:58,460
 i stipendija,

541
00:23:58,900 --> 00:23:59,900
 i škola,

542
00:23:59,900 --> 00:24:01,400
 znači 1598.

543
00:24:01,400 --> 00:24:02,260
 je napravljanje na školu

544
00:24:02,260 --> 00:24:03,720
 u Betlehemu,

545
00:24:03,720 --> 00:24:05,660
 kustodija sveto zemlji,

546
00:24:05,660 --> 00:24:06,020
 dakle,

547
00:24:06,020 --> 00:24:08,100
 tu najstariju školu ima

548
00:24:08,100 --> 00:24:09,520
 na cijelom bliskom istoku,

549
00:24:09,520 --> 00:24:10,280
 Elipa.

550
00:24:10,280 --> 00:24:11,100
 To je sve ono što je

551
00:24:11,100 --> 00:24:11,880
 stodjećima ovdje

552
00:24:11,880 --> 00:24:13,060
