573
00:24:36,240 --> 00:24:36,820
 a naravno,

574
00:24:36,820 --> 00:24:38,140
 ljudi su jako zahvalni,

575
00:24:38,140 --> 00:24:38,980
 što sam spomenula,

576
00:24:38,980 --> 00:24:40,580
 jako cijene,

577
00:24:40,580 --> 00:24:43,580
 i najmanju moguću pomoć,

578
00:24:43,580 --> 00:24:44,800
 već je njima to veliko,

579
00:24:45,280 --> 00:24:46,700
 jer prva stvar,

580
00:24:46,700 --> 00:24:47,280
 evo,

581
00:24:47,280 --> 00:24:48,220
