582
00:24:48,220 --> 00:24:49,820
 sam uspio doći u Spliti,

583
00:24:49,820 --> 00:24:51,600
 bili smo u Hrvatskoj cijeloj,

584
00:24:51,600 --> 00:24:53,360
 prvo si dječacima ovdje,

585
00:24:53,360 --> 00:24:54,020
 su iz doma,

586
00:24:54,020 --> 00:24:55,140
 i kad su vidjeli,

587
00:24:55,140 --> 00:24:56,280
 Frasandro,

588
00:24:56,280 --> 00:24:57,180
 pa ti se napustio,

589
00:24:57,180 --> 00:24:58,220
 napustio sve ovo

590
00:24:58,220 --> 00:24:59,720
 da dođeš ovdje kod nas,

591
00:24:59,720 --> 00:25:01,440
 jer ja rekao,

592
00:25:01,440 --> 00:25:01,740
 da,

593
00:25:01,740 --> 00:25:03,700
