594
00:25:03,700 --> 00:25:05,660
 jer naša je domovina

595
00:25:05,660 --> 00:25:06,360
 jako lijepa,

596
00:25:06,360 --> 00:25:08,180
 ali je i ovdje jako lijepo,

597
00:25:08,180 --> 00:25:08,380
 jel da?

598
00:25:08,380 --> 00:25:09,780
 Tako da,

599
00:25:09,780 --> 00:25:10,940
 jako je dobro

600
00:25:10,940 --> 00:25:12,280
 da oni to isto shvate,

601
00:25:12,280 --> 00:25:13,400
 da koliko god možda imali

602
00:25:13,400 --> 00:25:16,040
