605
00:25:18,140 --> 00:25:20,000
 da su ne znam kakve poteškoće,

606
00:25:20,000 --> 00:25:21,520
 ti se ovdje nalaziš.

607
00:25:21,520 --> 00:25:23,820
 Da, evo,

608
00:25:23,820 --> 00:25:25,500
 Franciscan Boys Home

609
00:25:25,500 --> 00:25:26,860
 je toliko meni u srcu,

610
00:25:26,860 --> 00:25:28,220
 tako da mi je ta tema

611
00:25:28,220 --> 00:25:29,600
 nekako ubiti

612
00:25:29,600 --> 00:25:31,140
 stalno obnavljanje

613
00:25:31,140 --> 00:25:32,900
 te emocije koje živim,

614
00:25:32,900 --> 00:25:35,020
 i osjećam se doista ovdje

615
00:25:35,020 --> 00:25:35,840
 kao doma,

616
00:25:35,840 --> 00:25:37,700
 tako da se nadam

617
00:25:37,700 --> 00:25:38,880
 da ću još mnogo puta

618
00:25:38,880 --> 00:25:40,900
 doći u svoju kuću,

619
00:25:40,900 --> 00:25:42,040
 u srcu Berlehema,

620
00:25:42,040 --> 00:25:43,100
 ovdje Berlehem

621
00:25:43,100 --> 00:25:44,600
 arapski,

622
00:25:44,600 --> 00:25:45,560
 znači kuća kruha,

623
00:25:45,560 --> 00:25:46,220
 ali tako,

624
00:25:46,220 --> 00:25:47,640
 zapravo tu nam je došao

625
00:25:47,640 --> 00:25:49,280
 Isus koji je kruh,

626
00:25:49,280 --> 00:25:49,540
 da,

627
00:25:49,540 --> 00:25:51,220
 jednak hebrejski,

628
00:25:51,220 --> 00:25:51,460
 aha,

629
00:25:51,460 --> 00:25:52,200
 kuća kruha,

630
00:25:52,200 --> 00:25:53,440
 odnosno kuća mesa,

631
00:25:53,440 --> 00:25:55,360
 ali zapravo to je to,

632
00:25:55,360 --> 00:25:56,680
 tu nam se gospodin

633
00:25:56,680 --> 00:25:57,480
 je li utjelovio,

634
00:25:57,480 --> 00:26:00,740
 ali osim Franciscan Boys Home-a

635
00:26:00,740 --> 00:26:01,120
 koji je,

636
00:26:01,120 --> 00:26:01,640
 ajmo reći,

637
00:26:01,640 --> 00:26:03,580
 ja bih ga osobno doživila

638
00:26:03,580 --> 00:26:05,100
 kao srce srca tvoga,

639
00:26:05,100 --> 00:26:06,340
 kao da je to ono

640
00:26:06,340 --> 00:26:08,220
 nekako

641
00:26:08,220 --> 00:26:09,740
 najdublje u tebi,

642
00:26:09,740 --> 00:26:11,480
