643
00:26:11,480 --> 00:26:12,440
 ranjena djetinstva,

644
00:26:12,640 --> 00:26:14,020
 svi koji rade s ranjenom djecom

645
00:26:14,020 --> 00:26:15,640
 znaju da je to najveća odgovornost

646
00:26:15,640 --> 00:26:16,280
 pred Bogom

647
00:26:16,280 --> 00:26:17,780
 za liječiti ih

648
00:26:17,780 --> 00:26:19,380
 i zapravo izući ono

649
00:26:19,380 --> 00:26:20,500
 najviše što možemo

650
00:26:20,500 --> 00:26:21,300
 da tim priliku

651
00:26:21,300 --> 00:26:22,140
 da u Bože ljubavi

652
00:26:22,140 --> 00:26:23,460
 odrastu i ostvare se,

653
00:26:23,460 --> 00:26:25,560
 ali uz to postoji još čitam niz

654
00:26:25,560 --> 00:26:27,020
 tvojih odgovornosti,

655
00:26:27,020 --> 00:26:27,740
 tvojih aktivnosti,

656
00:26:27,740 --> 00:26:29,600
 uloga u Svjetoj Zemlji,

657
00:26:29,600 --> 00:26:31,120
 pa je dosta neobično

658
00:26:31,120 --> 00:26:32,680
 kako ti to uopće stižeš,

659
00:26:32,680 --> 00:26:34,560
 član si upravnom viječa,

660
00:26:34,560 --> 00:26:35,380
 to se tako kaže,

661
00:26:35,380 --> 00:26:35,940
 ili tako,

662
00:26:35,940 --> 00:26:37,300
 kustodije Svete Zemlje,

663
00:26:37,300 --> 00:26:38,740
 ti si najmlađi tamo,

664
00:26:38,740 --> 00:26:39,300
 tako?

665
00:26:40,840 --> 00:26:41,420
 Ja uvijek kažem,

666
00:26:41,420 --> 00:26:42,880
 mladi hrvatski pranjevac,

667
00:26:42,880 --> 00:26:44,560
 jer smo nas dvoje generacije,

668
00:26:44,560 --> 00:26:46,420
 pa će to tako zauvijek

669
00:26:46,420 --> 00:26:48,300
 biti mladi hrvatski pranjevac.

670
00:26:48,300 --> 00:26:50,780
 Uz to si zadužna naravno

671
00:26:50,780 --> 00:26:52,500
 za zvanja u samoj kustodije

672
00:26:52,500 --> 00:26:53,500
 ovdje u Svjetoj Zemlji,

673
00:26:53,500 --> 00:26:56,500
