679
00:27:07,300 --> 00:27:09,080
 u prvom redu naravno katolike.

680
00:27:09,660 --> 00:27:11,700
 I evo, nedavno je i hrvatska vlada

681
00:27:11,700 --> 00:27:13,900
 participirala velikom donacijom,

682
00:27:13,900 --> 00:27:15,960
 na čemu smo i naravno zahvalni

683
00:27:15,960 --> 00:27:17,560
