701
00:27:55,480 --> 00:27:59,600
 neki dan je jedan mladi čovjek u formaciji,

702
00:27:59,600 --> 00:28:00,720
 Franjevačko, rekao,

703
00:28:00,720 --> 00:28:03,020
 Frasandro je spasio moj poziv,

704
00:28:03,020 --> 00:28:05,820
 on je baš bio Boži glas u mom životu

705
00:28:05,820 --> 00:28:09,960
 i ono koliko si toga svjestan,

706
00:28:09,960 --> 00:28:11,520
 odnosno koliko si svjestan te odgovornosti,

707
00:28:11,520 --> 00:28:15,000
 da zapravo neke male, sitne riječi

708
00:28:15,000 --> 00:28:19,300
 koje nas začine ponekad kao samo dio svakodnevnog govora

709
00:28:19,300 --> 00:28:23,520
 mogu u nečem srcu toista promijeniti perspektivu

710
00:28:24,240 --> 00:28:26,220
 i zapravo percepciju poziva,

711
00:28:26,220 --> 00:28:27,980
 evo, to me baš zanima,

712
00:28:27,980 --> 00:28:30,340
 jer evo, to me baš ganulo kako je on to rekao,

713
00:28:30,340 --> 00:28:32,340
 Frasandro je spasio moj poziv.

714
00:28:32,340 --> 00:28:35,840
 Pa, Bogu, hvala,

715
00:28:35,840 --> 00:28:38,400
 sigurno da nisam ja, nego je Bog,

716
00:28:38,400 --> 00:28:40,980
 možda je korist je moje usne,

717
00:28:40,980 --> 00:28:43,100
 ne znam što je to točno bilo,

718
00:28:43,100 --> 00:28:44,400
 da me njemu u to ovoga,

719
00:28:44,400 --> 00:28:47,400
 da, ni stražit ćemo.

720
00:28:47,400 --> 00:28:49,680
 Pa sigurno, e, gle, ovako,

721
00:28:49,680 --> 00:28:52,180
 mi smo jedna obitelja ovdje,

722
00:28:52,180 --> 00:28:53,840
 hkotovo ka Franjevci, živimo,

723
00:28:54,240 --> 00:28:58,060
 osamstoljeća i preko šestdeset nacija

724
00:28:58,060 --> 00:28:59,340
 i to je u biti,

725
00:28:59,340 --> 00:29:01,900
 ovdje sam oskar je zapravo bogatstvo

726
00:29:01,900 --> 00:29:03,020
 Franjevaškog reda.

727
00:29:03,020 --> 00:29:05,360
 Poznaš jednog iz Brazila,

728
00:29:05,360 --> 00:29:07,260
 pa jednog iz Južne Koreje,

729
00:29:07,260 --> 00:29:09,200
 Frahtra, pa ne znam, Australije,

730
00:29:09,200 --> 00:29:10,880
 cijelog svijeta, Afrika i tako.

731
00:29:10,880 --> 00:29:13,820
 Koliko je to snažno,

732
00:29:13,820 --> 00:29:14,940
 svjedočanstvo, kad vidiš da

733
00:29:14,940 --> 00:29:16,500
 Franjevašk to nije življeno,

734
00:29:16,500 --> 00:29:17,880
 možda samo u našim okvirima,

735
00:29:17,880 --> 00:29:19,700
 jer puno puta smo mi zatvoreni

736
00:29:19,700 --> 00:29:21,100
 u neke naše okvire

737
00:29:21,100 --> 00:29:22,520
 i možda smo ono malo nacije,

738
00:29:22,520 --> 00:29:23,880
 mala nacija, pa mislimo, ono,

739
00:29:24,100 --> 00:29:27,040
 da je naš model upravo taj najuspješniji.

740
00:29:27,040 --> 00:29:28,680
 Ne znači ništa,

741
00:29:28,680 --> 00:29:31,760
 koliko zapravo bog se želi proslaviti.

742
00:29:31,760 --> 00:29:33,080
 Ovdje, isto kao župri vikar,

743
00:29:33,080 --> 00:29:35,920
 sam puno puta vidio da doista

744
00:29:35,920 --> 00:29:37,460
 bog se proslavlja.

745
00:29:37,460 --> 00:29:38,120
 Toliko.

746
00:29:38,120 --> 00:29:40,220
 Evo, bit svega je,

747
00:29:40,220 --> 00:29:42,200
 evo, i u ovom postoralu zvanja,

748
00:29:42,200 --> 00:29:44,140
 uvijek imati ono

749
00:29:44,140 --> 00:29:45,560
 da budeš svjedočanstvo.

750
00:29:45,560 --> 00:29:47,540
 Možda jedino što kaže Sveti Franjo,

751
00:29:47,540 --> 00:29:50,160
 ćeš biti jedina Biblija

752
00:29:50,160 --> 00:29:51,340
 koju će drugi pročitac.

753
00:29:52,100 --> 00:29:54,040
 Dakle, bilo koja je ta jedna tvoja riječi,

754
00:29:54,040 --> 00:29:55,720
 isto ti kao Anita,

755
00:29:55,720 --> 00:29:57,420
 sutra ćeš zavrati u domovinu,

756
00:29:57,420 --> 00:29:59,540
 jedna tvoja riječi je promijeniti možda nekoga

757
00:29:59,540 --> 00:30:01,020
 koju možda ne poznaješ.

758
00:30:01,020 --> 00:30:02,900
 Možda bez riječi,

759
00:30:02,900 --> 00:30:03,760
 samo što vidi tebe,

760
00:30:03,760 --> 00:30:05,080
 zna Isus je živ.

761
00:30:05,220 --> 00:30:07,000
 To je tako važno.

762
00:30:07,000 --> 00:30:10,500
 Zato je to autentičnost

763
00:30:10,500 --> 00:30:12,200
 našeg kršanskog poziva

764
00:30:12,200 --> 00:30:14,760
 je živjeti Božju riječ

765
00:30:14,760 --> 00:30:16,020
 koja se odio ti lovela

766
00:30:16,020 --> 00:30:16,840
 i odpili.

767
00:30:16,840 --> 00:30:18,900
 I to mi kao Franjovci

768
00:30:18,900 --> 00:30:20,620
 živimo kao obitelj,

769
00:30:20,620 --> 00:30:22,520
 isto tako je ovdje djeca u domu

770
00:30:22,520 --> 00:30:24,080
 i u katoličkoj akciji

771
00:30:24,080 --> 00:30:25,800
 koja je jedina zapravo,

772
00:30:25,800 --> 00:30:28,540
 jedino mjesto gdje se mogu kršani susretati,

773
00:30:28,540 --> 00:30:30,100
 susretati je naravno i ostali,

774
00:30:30,100 --> 00:30:32,300
 poreko sportskih aktivnosti,

775
00:30:32,300 --> 00:30:33,380
 imokulturni centar,

776
00:30:33,380 --> 00:30:34,700
 ogrom ne vidjela si

777
00:30:34,700 --> 00:30:36,740
 toliko toga ima za napraviti.

778
00:30:36,740 --> 00:30:39,920
 I samo ono što su malo prije spomenuli,

779
00:30:39,920 --> 00:30:42,540
 Hrvati su prisutni u već stoljećima,

780
00:30:42,540 --> 00:30:44,340
 samo neozumno Gecemani

781
00:30:44,340 --> 00:30:47,200
 koji je zbog hrvatskih Hrvata,

782
00:30:47,200 --> 00:30:50,320
 trojice, braće Branković i Sarajeva

783
00:30:50,320 --> 00:30:52,520
 darovali su kustodiju.

784
00:30:52,520 --> 00:30:54,580
 Pa onda je ono brdo tabor gdje spačava,

785
00:30:54,580 --> 00:30:58,300
 onda ono drvo ispačava

786
00:30:58,300 --> 00:30:59,100
 u krovište,

787
00:30:59,100 --> 00:31:01,220
 pa onda ima toliko vratara

788
00:31:01,220 --> 00:31:03,980
 koji su bili i kustodi ovdje u Svjetoj zemlji

789
00:31:03,980 --> 00:31:04,920
 i povijestičari

790
00:31:04,920 --> 00:31:09,000
 i opet koji su brdo nebo kupili,

791
00:31:09,000 --> 00:31:10,940
 toliko mogli bi nam brajati,

792
00:31:10,940 --> 00:31:14,380
 ali to je ono prisutstvo naše domovine ovdje.

793
00:31:14,380 --> 00:31:15,760
 Jer mi kao domovina,

794
00:31:15,760 --> 00:31:18,020
 naša domovina ono na nebesima,

795
00:31:18,020 --> 00:31:19,860
 ali ovdje znamo da Isus živio.

796
00:31:19,860 --> 00:31:22,860
 Dakle da jedan počulek dođe u Svjetoj zemlji,

797
00:31:22,860 --> 00:31:23,640
 u zemlju,

798
00:31:23,640 --> 00:31:25,720
 on će shvatiti ove riječi možda malo dubnje,

799
00:31:25,720 --> 00:31:27,760
 a sigurno će biti ovdje koji će slušati

800
00:31:28,060 --> 00:31:29,740
 vidjeti ovaj video,

801
00:31:29,740 --> 00:31:30,960
 pa će vidjeti,

802
00:31:30,960 --> 00:31:33,600
 pa da, znamo o čemu razgovaraju,

803
00:31:33,600 --> 00:31:34,760
 tamo sam ja to vidio.

804
00:31:36,060 --> 00:31:37,520
 Da, to je živa istina,

805
00:31:37,520 --> 00:31:39,880
 obično kad putujem po svijetu,

806
00:31:39,880 --> 00:31:41,600
 onda kažem Hrvatska,

807
00:31:41,600 --> 00:31:42,020
 onda svi,

808
00:31:42,020 --> 00:31:44,000
 a Luka Modrić ili Prijeto,

809
00:31:44,000 --> 00:31:44,780
 Vilo Šuker,

810
00:31:44,780 --> 00:31:47,420
 ali u Svjetoj zemlji kad kažeš Hrvatska,

811
00:31:47,420 --> 00:31:47,840
 onda kažu,

812
00:31:47,840 --> 00:31:49,000
 a Buna Sandra.

813
00:31:51,000 --> 00:31:51,920
 vidiš ti da,

814
00:31:51,920 --> 00:31:53,960
 a pa to je tako,

815
00:31:53,960 --> 00:31:54,220
 mislim,

816
00:31:54,220 --> 00:31:55,820
 nećemo sad uopće,

817
00:31:55,820 --> 00:31:57,820
 tako da evo,

818
00:31:57,820 --> 00:31:58,860
 kad bi Bog imao,

819
00:31:58,860 --> 00:32:02,120
 ili kad bi države imale veleposlanika ljubavi,

820
00:32:02,120 --> 00:32:03,260
 onda bi ti sigurno,

821
00:32:03,260 --> 00:32:04,940
 imao to vijesto,

822
00:32:04,940 --> 00:32:05,940
 jer to u biti,

823
00:32:05,940 --> 00:32:07,920
 u biti u ovom boys homu,

824
00:32:07,920 --> 00:32:08,880
 to i je tako,

825
00:32:08,880 --> 00:32:10,700
 ta ljubav je doista življena,

826
00:32:10,700 --> 00:32:12,420
 uvijek svako jutro kad se probudim,

827
00:32:12,420 --> 00:32:14,200
 pa krenem kroz vrton,

828
00:32:14,200 --> 00:32:14,760
 da kažem,

829
00:32:14,760 --> 00:32:17,020
 a Sveti Frane bi sad ovdje reka,

830
00:32:17,020 --> 00:32:18,700
 ljubav je ovdje ljubljena,

831
00:32:18,700 --> 00:32:21,540
 i mislim da to zapravo je promjena,

832
00:32:21,540 --> 00:32:23,220
 te paradigme tog osjećaja,

833
00:32:23,220 --> 00:32:24,180
 koji je on imao,

834
00:32:24,180 --> 00:32:26,160
 te žalosti nad Isusovim križom,

835
00:32:26,160 --> 00:32:27,720
 da nismo bili sposobni,

836
00:32:27,720 --> 00:32:29,400
 kapacitirani ljubiti ljubav,

837
00:32:29,400 --> 00:32:31,560
 a sad jednom dođeš na mjesto,

838
00:32:31,560 --> 00:32:33,160
 gdje je doista njegov,

839
00:32:33,160 --> 00:32:33,460
 mislim,

840
00:32:33,460 --> 00:32:34,280
 Franji sin,

841
00:32:34,280 --> 00:32:35,060
 odnosno ti,

842
00:32:35,060 --> 00:32:36,980
 je onaj koji stvara ambijent,

843
00:32:36,980 --> 00:32:38,220
 u kojem je ljubav ljubljena,

844
00:32:38,220 --> 00:32:39,980
 i to mi je tako divno,

845
00:32:40,040 --> 00:32:41,880
 i to je ono zapravo što te uzme,

846
00:32:41,880 --> 00:32:43,000
 i nekako nahrani,

847
00:32:43,000 --> 00:32:45,240
 i imaš osjećaj da ćeš od toga moći odlomiti,

848
00:32:45,240 --> 00:32:47,020
 dati taj kruh drugim ljudima,

849
00:32:47,020 --> 00:32:48,800
 koji su sretneš,

850
00:32:48,800 --> 00:32:49,200
 tako da,

851
00:32:49,200 --> 00:32:50,140
 hvala na tome.

852
00:32:50,140 --> 00:32:51,200
 Ali evo,

853
00:32:51,200 --> 00:32:52,720
 sad bih htjela još nešto,

854
00:32:52,720 --> 00:32:55,560
 ljudi su jako u Hrvatskoj prestrašani,

855
00:32:55,560 --> 00:32:56,220
 i općenito,

856
00:32:56,220 --> 00:32:59,980
 zapadni svijet je pod medijskim terorom,

857
00:32:59,980 --> 00:33:01,180
 ja bih se usudila reći,

858
00:33:01,180 --> 00:33:03,220
 i bez ikakvih političkih konotacija,

859
00:33:03,220 --> 00:33:06,320
 želim samo razgovarati o situaciji u Svetoj zemlji,

860
00:33:06,320 --> 00:33:07,480
 jako puno ljudi je,

861
00:33:10,040 --> 00:33:12,340
 i prvi koji je bio za uskrsi ovaj sada,

862
00:33:12,340 --> 00:33:13,100
 malo duži,

863
00:33:13,100 --> 00:33:16,060
 su ili jako prestrašeni,

864
00:33:16,060 --> 00:33:16,460
 i rekli,

865
00:33:16,460 --> 00:33:19,560
 sad nije vrijeme zaputovati u Svetu zemlju,

866
00:33:19,560 --> 00:33:22,360
 a cijelo vrijeme čujemo pozive

867
00:33:22,360 --> 00:33:25,480
 i od prekrasnog ovdje patrijarha,

868
00:33:25,480 --> 00:33:28,400
 latinskog Pierbatiste Pizzabale,

869
00:33:28,400 --> 00:33:31,340
 koji stalno poziva kršane da dođu u Svetu zemlju,

870
00:33:31,340 --> 00:33:35,280
 jer većina ljudi ovdje ipak na direktan ili indirektan način,

871
00:33:35,280 --> 00:33:36,760
 osobito na zapadne ovali,

872
00:33:36,760 --> 00:33:38,420
 živi od turizma,

873
00:33:38,540 --> 00:33:41,100
 ili od prodaje, od suvenira, hotela,

874
00:33:41,100 --> 00:33:44,460
 različiti uvostiteljskih usluga,

875
00:33:44,460 --> 00:33:46,200
 i naravno već godinu i koliko,

876
00:33:46,200 --> 00:33:47,660
 dva, tri mjeseca u biti,

877
00:33:47,660 --> 00:33:50,700
 to izostaje i ljudima je jako teško.

878
00:33:50,700 --> 00:33:51,160
 Pa evo,

879
00:33:51,160 --> 00:33:54,660
 iz tvoje perspektive nekoga ko živio u stvarnost,

880
00:33:54,660 --> 00:33:56,320
 ja sam tu ipak kraće,

881
00:33:56,320 --> 00:33:58,640
 koji su temeljni problemi,

882
00:33:59,280 --> 00:34:06,940
 kako se može zaustaviti odlazak ljudi Arapa kršena iz ovog dijela svijeta sada ovim teškim okolnostima,

883
00:34:06,940 --> 00:34:11,440
 jer znamo to po hrvatskom modelu, ljudi kada odu jako se teško vraćaju.

884
00:34:12,160 --> 00:34:14,660
 I što bi bila tvoja poruka Hrvatima,

885
00:34:14,660 --> 00:34:16,400
 znači našim ljudima u domovini,

886
00:34:16,400 --> 00:34:18,620
 kako bi trebali imati odnosi,

887
00:34:18,620 --> 00:34:21,020
 i evo, slobodno ih možeš pozvati da se ohrabre,

888
00:34:21,020 --> 00:34:21,560
 da dođe,

889
00:34:21,560 --> 00:34:25,320
 ja mogu posvjedoći da ne postoji nijedna kulisa,

890
00:34:25,320 --> 00:34:27,240
 koja može bi alternativa miru,

891
00:34:27,240 --> 00:34:29,280
 koji mi ovdje zapravo živimo,

892
00:34:29,280 --> 00:34:33,040
 Prva stvar,

893
00:34:33,040 --> 00:34:35,260
 evo, u ovih godine,

894
00:34:35,260 --> 00:34:37,900
 par mjeseci i koliko je ovo traje ovaj rat i tako,

895
00:34:37,900 --> 00:34:40,180
 nije bila trenutka da

896
00:34:40,180 --> 00:34:43,500
 hodočasnici su bile nekoj opasnosti.

897
00:34:43,500 --> 00:34:45,020
 Tako je.

898
00:34:45,020 --> 00:34:47,400
 Grupe od početaka samih

899
00:34:47,400 --> 00:34:49,860
 nisu prestajale dolaziti.

900
00:34:49,860 --> 00:34:51,960
 Naravno, možda iz Europa manje,

901
00:34:51,960 --> 00:34:53,260
 iz Europe dolaze,

902
00:34:53,260 --> 00:34:54,740
 ali ne toliko kao ora prije.

903
00:34:54,740 --> 00:34:56,640
 Ali evo, hvala Bogu,

904
00:34:56,640 --> 00:34:58,680
 sad ima dobrih pomaka i naznaka.

905
00:34:59,280 --> 00:35:01,560
 od početka ovog mjeseca

906
00:35:01,560 --> 00:35:02,540
 do biti sredine,

907
00:35:02,540 --> 00:35:05,160
 puno tih zrakopalovih kompanija

908
00:35:05,160 --> 00:35:05,960
 se vraćaju.

909
00:35:05,960 --> 00:35:08,340
 Prva stvar, druga stvar,

910
00:35:08,340 --> 00:35:10,880
 naravno da je mediji to malo na bušu.

911
00:35:10,880 --> 00:35:13,480
 Puno puta sam ja to rekao

912
00:35:13,480 --> 00:35:14,100
 od početaka,

913
00:35:14,100 --> 00:35:15,840
 kada su evo neke medijske kuće

914
00:35:15,840 --> 00:35:17,320
 mene zpitali iz izjeva,

915
00:35:17,320 --> 00:35:17,920
 sam rekao,

916
00:35:17,920 --> 00:35:19,020
 nemojte se bojati,

917
00:35:19,020 --> 00:35:19,880
 dođete uvijek.

918
00:35:19,880 --> 00:35:22,260
 Nije tako uvijek kao što je

919
00:35:22,260 --> 00:35:24,080
 vidite na televiziji i u medijima.

920
00:35:24,080 --> 00:35:25,060
 Nije sve tako.

921
00:35:25,060 --> 00:35:26,180
 Svi znamo da je,

922
00:35:26,180 --> 00:35:27,620
 svi znamo iz prve ruke

923
00:35:27,620 --> 00:35:28,600
 koliko puta vidiš

924
00:35:28,600 --> 00:35:29,360
 jednu vijest.

925
00:35:29,360 --> 00:35:30,760
 Ti kad si na terenu,

926
00:35:30,760 --> 00:35:31,740
 nekada je što te lizi,

927
00:35:31,740 --> 00:35:33,020
 da su to dvije

928
00:35:33,020 --> 00:35:36,220
 proporcionalne stvari.

929
00:35:36,220 --> 00:35:39,660
 Nemaju ovoga

930
00:35:39,660 --> 00:35:40,900
 jedne veze,

931
00:35:40,900 --> 00:35:41,580
 jedna s drugom.

932
00:35:41,580 --> 00:35:43,400
 A naravno,

933
00:35:43,400 --> 00:35:46,780
 kao tako,

934
00:35:46,780 --> 00:35:47,760
 na taj način,

935
00:35:47,760 --> 00:35:49,420
 pogotovo sada,

936
00:35:49,420 --> 00:35:50,300
 kad čovjek dođe,

937
00:35:50,300 --> 00:35:51,500
 može ostati na svjetim mjestima

938
00:35:51,500 --> 00:35:51,960
 i duže.

939
00:35:51,960 --> 00:35:53,560
 Nemo na trčanja,

940
00:35:53,560 --> 00:35:54,600
 vakacijona,

941
00:35:54,600 --> 00:35:55,980
 naput moraju posjediti

942
00:35:55,980 --> 00:35:58,100
 ajmo idemo dalje.

943
00:35:58,160 --> 00:35:58,280
 ne.

944
00:35:58,280 --> 00:35:59,920
